[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "ふううう……終わった～……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01240",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "目立ったミスもなかったし、良かったんじゃない？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_01241",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "観客のみんなも盛り上がってくれていたようでござる！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01242",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "三人とも、素晴らしいライブでしたわ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_01243",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "社長殿！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01244",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "トップバッターという大役、\n見事に果たしてみせましたわね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_01245",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "……ええ。これで思い残すことはありませぬ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01246",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01247",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "……やだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_01248",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "これで終わりなんてやだ！\n辞めないで……もっと一緒にアイドルやりたい……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_01249",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "ヨハナ……すまぬ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01250",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "……謝らないで。わがままだって分かってるから……\nでも……うっ、ぐす……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_01251",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "実はね、ライブの前にヨハナや社長と話してたんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01252",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "今後、『Ｃｕｔｉｅ☆ＡｎｉｍａＬ』を\nどうするのかって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01253",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "っ……！　どうするつもりなのだ……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01254",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "辞めないよ。二人になっても活動を続ける",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01255",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "『Ｃｕｔｉｅ☆ＡｎｉｍａＬ』はなくならない。\nだから……戻りたくなったら、いつでも戻って来てよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01256",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "アタシたち、待ってるから……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01257",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "っ……ありがとう、みんな……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01258",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "ありがとう……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01259",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "さ、フェスはまだ終わっていませんわ。\n幕が下りるまで、大いに楽しみましょう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_01260",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "司会",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "さあ！　今年も残すところ１分を切りました！\nカウントダウンのご用意を！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_717_504_01261",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
